*{{IPA|/ˈmeɪnʤə/}}
*{{SAMPA|/"meIndZ@/}}
*'''Hyphenation:''' man·ger
*'''Rhymes:''' [[Rhymes:English:-eɪndʒə|-eɪndʒə]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A trough for animals to eat from.

